clang++ -std=c++23 prog.cpp -o prog.exe -Wall -Wextra -ggdb -Weffc++ -Wconversion -Wsign-conversion -Werror

clang++ -> compiler
-std=c++23 -> c+= version
-o -> output file name
-Wall -> enable most commonly used warnings
-Wextra -> enable extra warnings that are not used in -Wall
-ggdb -> generate debugging information optimized for gdb
-Weffc++ -> Warn about effects about Scott Mayers Effective c++ guidelines
-Wconversion -> Warn about implicit type conversions and may change values
-Wsign-conversion -> Warn when signedness changes during conversions
-Werror -> treat every warnings as compilation error
-O2 -> seocnd level optmization
-march=native -> optimize for current cpu
-mtune=native -> optimize scheduling for cpu
-ffast-math -> ignore IEEE-754 rules to generate faster code

